window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In the year 2280, an alien fleet attacked the Earth. Their weapons were unstoppable, their defenses unbreakable. Our technology was inferior, our militaries overwhelmed. Only one starship escaped before civilization fell. </p> <p>Earth was lost. It was never forgotten. </p> <p>Fifty-two years have passed. A message from home has been received. The time to fight for what is ours has come. </p> <p>Welcome to the rebellion. </p>"; 
